    <section_number>34</section_number>
    <catch_line>Proxies</catch_line>
    <order_by>34</order_by>
    <text>
        Absent stockholders may vote at all meetings by proxy, authorized in writing, which shall be executed and dated within six months previous to the meeting at which it is used.
    </text>
